des:
Rain sounds play the sound of rain in your Alexa device. To start using rain sounds in Alexa device just enable the skill in Alexa and say, Alexa, play rain sounds.

If you enjoy the skill, please do leave us a review as it helps other people find it and enjoy the skill too
